TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed FtpStatusCode extends System.Enum

summary.span: 指定檔案傳輸通訊協定 (FTP) 作業傳回的狀態碼。

span.span: Specifies the status codes returned for a File Transfer Protocol (FTP) operation.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 列舉會定義傳回的值屬性。The enumeration defines the values returned in the property. 如需有關 FTP 伺服器的狀態碼的詳細資訊，請參閱[RFC 959:「 檔案傳輸通訊協定 」，區段 4.2:「 FTP 回覆 「](https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc959.txt)。For additional information about FTP server status codes, see [RFC 959: "File Transfer Protocol", Section 4.2: "FTP Replies"](https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc959.txt). ## Examples 下列程式碼範例會將傳送至 FTP 伺服器上建立新目錄的 FTP 要求，並檢查回應中傳回的狀態碼。The following code example sends an FTP request to make a new directory on an FTP server and checks the status code returned in the response. [!code-cpp[NclFtpClient#22](~/samples/snippets/cpp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/NCLFtpClient/CPP/ftptests.cpp#22)] [!code-csharp[NclFtpClient#22](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_Remoting/NCLFtpClient/CS/ftptests.cs#22)]
